---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Press Release: Fortune 500 #1 Best Company to Work For"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation is named Fortune 500 #1 Best Company to Work For in 2037, recognized for innovation culture, employee benefits, and career development programs."
  type="article"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- ARTICLE HEADER -->
    <section class="relative py-20 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <a href="/news" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            &larr; BACK TO NEWSROOM
          </a>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] tracking-widest bg-[#FFC600]/10 px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CORPORATE</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 tracking-wider">PRESS RELEASE</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase leading-none mb-6">
            WEYLAND-YUTANI NAMED FORTUNE 500 <span class="text-[#FFC600]">#1 BEST COMPANY TO WORK FOR</span>
          </h1>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">
            <span>MARCH 15, 2037</span>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600]">|</span>
            <span>NEW YORK, NY</span>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600]">|</span>
            <span>FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 hazard-stripes-thin h-1"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- ARTICLE BODY -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-black">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-base">
            <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold">
              <strong>NEW YORK --</strong> Fortune magazine today named Weyland-Yutani Corporation (NYSE: WEYU) the #1 Best Company to Work For on its 2037 Fortune 500 ranking, recognizing the Corporation for exceptional workplace culture, industry-leading employee benefits, and an unmatched commitment to professional development and career advancement. This marks the first time Weyland-Yutani has received the top ranking, though the Corporation has appeared in the top 10 for seven consecutive years.
            </p>

            <p>
              The Fortune ranking evaluates companies across five dimensions: compensation and financial benefits, workplace culture and employee satisfaction, professional development and career mobility, innovation environment, and work-life integration. Weyland-Yutani achieved the highest score ever recorded in the categories of innovation environment and career mobility, reflecting the Corporation's unique ability to offer employees career paths that span continents, industries, and worlds.
            </p>

            <p>
              "Our people are our capability," said Karl Bishop Weyland, Chief Executive Officer of Weyland-Yutani Corporation. "Every ship we build, every world we terraform, every breakthrough we achieve begins with a person who chose to bring their talent and ambition to this Corporation. This recognition belongs to every one of our employees, from the research laboratories in San Francisco to the atmospheric processors on the frontier."
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase mt-12 mb-4">BENEFITS AND COMPENSATION</h2>
            <div class="h-px w-24 bg-[#FFC600] mb-6"></div>

            <!-- BENEFITS DATA -->
            <div class="my-8 corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600] uppercase mb-6">EMPLOYEE BENEFITS -- HIGHLIGHTS</h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">01</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">COMPREHENSIVE HEALTHCARE</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">100% COVERAGE, INCLUDING MEDPOD ACCESS FOR ALL EMPLOYEES AND DEPENDENTS</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">02</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">EDUCATION SUPPORT</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">FULL TUITION REIMBURSEMENT AND STUDENT LOAN REPAYMENT UP TO $200,000</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">03</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">RETIREMENT PROGRAM</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">15% COMPANY MATCH ON ALL RETIREMENT CONTRIBUTIONS, VESTED IMMEDIATELY</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">04</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">PARENTAL LEAVE</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">26 WEEKS PAID LEAVE FOR ALL NEW PARENTS, REGARDLESS OF GENDER</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">05</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">OFF-WORLD ASSIGNMENT BONUSES</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">200-500% BASE SALARY PREMIUM FOR COLONY AND DEEP-SPACE POSTINGS</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">06</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">$18,000 ANNUAL TRAINING BUDGET PER EMPLOYEE, PLUS INTERNAL UNIVERSITY ACCESS</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">07</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">EQUITY PARTICIPATION</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">STOCK GRANTS FOR ALL EMPLOYEES AT EVERY LEVEL, FROM ENTRY TO EXECUTIVE</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs mt-0.5">08</span>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">HOUSING ASSISTANCE</div>
                      <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-1">SUBSIDIZED HOUSING AT ALL COLONY INSTALLATIONS AND MAJOR EARTH CAMPUSES</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase mt-12 mb-4">CULTURE OF INNOVATION</h2>
            <div class="h-px w-24 bg-[#FFC600] mb-6"></div>

            <p>
              Fortune's assessment particularly noted the Corporation's "innovation culture," in which employees at all levels are encouraged and resourced to pursue novel solutions to operational challenges. The Corporation's internal Innovation Grant Program has funded more than 14,000 employee-originated projects since its inception, of which 2,300 have resulted in patented technologies or operational improvements that have been adopted Corporation-wide.
            </p>

            <p>
              "What sets Weyland-Yutani apart is that innovation is not confined to the R&D lab," said Fortune Editor-in-Chief Mariana Santos. "A maintenance technician on a colony installation has the same access to innovation funding as a senior scientist in San Francisco. The Corporation has built a system where good ideas can come from anywhere and reach the people who can implement them."
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase mt-12 mb-4">WORKFORCE STATISTICS</h2>
            <div class="h-px w-24 bg-[#FFC600] mb-6"></div>

            <div class="my-8 corp-card p-8">
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">94%</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2">EMPLOYEE SATISFACTION RATE</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">8.2 YR</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2">AVERAGE TENURE</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">72%</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2">INTERNAL PROMOTION RATE</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">127</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2">NATIONALITIES REPRESENTED</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Weyland-Yutani Corporation currently employs approximately 1.2 million people across 52 countries and more than 40 off-world installations. The Corporation received 8.4 million job applications in the last fiscal year, reflecting a selectivity rate of approximately 1.2%.
            </p>

            <!-- BOILERPLATE -->
            <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">ABOUT WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATION</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                Weyland-Yutani Corporation is a British-Japanese multinational conglomerate and the global leader in terraforming, cybernetics, defense, energy, health sciences, biological research, and electronics. Headquartered in San Francisco with major operations in Tokyo and the Sea of Tranquility, Luna. NYSE: WEYU.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 mt-8">MEDIA CONTACT</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                Corporate Communications<br/>
                media@weylandyutani.com<br/>
                +1-800-555-WYCO
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
